Author: escapingdaybyday
Text: I've been able to keep liquids down for a minute now and idk it's just weird to me

Author: throwawayedfeelz
Text: If you were throwing up I'd say it's likely that all your electrolytes are out of whack and in turn you're retaining water, as well as just in general water retention from sickness - I'm exactly the same when I get super pukey sick I gain at first but then drop down lower when I start being able to keep.liquids down again
